data.description: This home is located in the quaint little town of Bonanza. Only about 23 miles from Klamath Falls. 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with just over 1100 square feet with a nice floor plan and attached garage. Close to a country convenience store, restaurant, gas station, school, and just a few blocks from the park! Country atmosphere everywhere around this town.
